import React from 'react'
import NavBar from './NavBar'
import ChatsList from './ChatsList'
import { styled } from '@mui/system'

const Container = styled('div')({
  height: '100vh'
})


const ChatsListScreen: React.FC = () => (
  <Container>
    <NavBar />
    <ChatsList />
  </Container>
)

export default ChatsListScreen
